data.title: Tacoma, Washington
data.meta_description: Bird's-eye view. Stamped on: From Russell J. Joy, real estate loans, 1710 Pacific Avenue, Tacoma, Wash. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. Includes index to points of interest, inset of "Tacoma in 1878," and ill. of selected buildings in margins. Vault PM3 Acquisitions control no. 60-83
